Ancelotti asked if Calvert-Lewin's miss changed the game: &quot;No, the game was already over in the first minute.&quot; <br />
<br />
Ancelotti: &quot;Everything went wrong. It is not difficult to judge this game or analyse this game. We were too open defensively, we lost a lot of duels, we made a lot of mistakes with the ball. It was not a good day. What we can do is learn from our mistakes.&quot;
